longBusinessSummary: Zurvita Holdings, Inc. markets health and wellness products in the United States, Hong Kong, Canada, Singapore, Australia, the United Kingdom, and the Dominican Republic. Its principal products comprise Zeal Wellness, an antioxidants and vitamins nutritional product in wild berry and bold grape flavors; Zeal Advanced Formula Protein Shakes, a source of dietary fiber in chocolate delight and vanilla crème flavors; Zeal cleanse, a herbal and probiotic cleanse; and Zeal burn, a thermogenic fat burner. The company sells its products through its network of independent sales consultants. Zurvita Holdings, Inc. was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas. Zurvita Holdings, Inc. is a subsidiary of The Amacore Group, Inc.
